The paper proposes a machine learning algorithm for training TSK fuzzy classifiers, which is a topic related to machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also introduces two novel techniques, uniform regularization and batch normalization, which are commonly used in neural networks and deep learning (cs.NE, cs.SI). Additionally, the experiments involve classification tasks on various datasets, which could be related to computer vision (cs.CV).
